text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Tazlarovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Isyangulovo, 3 km from Tazlarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Ivanovka, Zianchurinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
